sbmlme.converter

Class MEJsonReactionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • sbmlme.converter.MEJsonReactionType

  • public class MEJsonReactionType
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the different types of reactions in a COBRAme JSON schema. Any reactions in a COBRAme model needs to have one and only one of the declared types in this class.
    Author:
    Marc A. Voigt
